{"tid":177062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老老柒柒，香港有咩地方值得推介比旅客去？","createTime":"2017-03-28T14:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T16:40:47.000Z","uid":41412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"baa5304efd10329fd5eb613b3073c2d55807ee3e","tid":177062,"uid":41412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"有個日本朋友準備黎香港，佢問我香港有咩地方介紹。佢行程預左七日，有一日去迪士尼，除左山頂呢d行到冇人有地方，巴/絲打有咩好推介"},{"pid":"39c303448cb61ae25a8ce55cfcc2d611c84db228","tid":177062,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"嚟香港唔係唔去掃街呀嘛"},{"pid":"8e18bc6ae3fbd2886e008f5519256d9b623dd9a4","tid":177062,"uid":19116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"帶佢去燒野食 記住用叉燒"},{"pid":"4c0273028b2f288a4a59e806002731917b0a37a0","tid":177062,"uid":41412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚟香港唔係唔去掃街呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n有冇d地方介紹，好多專劏遊客一筆"},{"pid":"777607a6c7ac2c526365de363bc20d7f9fe7f762","tid":177062,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"大澳"},{"pid":"e980c20cb9cfa86fecf3c0851aed56722d1ff9e8","tid":177062,"uid":34032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶佢去燒野食 記住用叉燒</blockquote><br />\n呢個幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0013f0e9dd72ee95816cdce72252a12ebf199ba8","tid":177062,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"玩海馬公園 迪迪尼<br />\n行尖咀 港島由上環掃到北角<br />\n食野落深水埗旺角佐敦油地<br />\n基本上旅客黎香港 剩係去港鐵 藍紅色線地方就得<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a50ff74309cef7a2fb4bec8e2a721c13826c2b","tid":177062,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"龍脊"},{"pid":"b39bb44ea2a8357c42b1cc8427a6829973954d92","tid":177062,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嚟香港唔係唔去掃街呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n有冇d地方介紹，好多專劏遊客一筆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n掃街都係油麻地登打士街一帶/ 西灣河太安樓/ 葵廣<br />\n銅鑼灣d街邊嘢食太貴了<br />\n<br />\n另外你可以帶佢試下去上環蓮香居，試下推車仔茶樓一盅兩件<br />\n地道d又平民d嘅，可以試中環大排檔勝香園，d蕃茄麵真係全港最好食，不過超多人排隊<br />\n又或者帶佢去食澳牛感受下快餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同食大家都愛嘅譚仔"}]}